{
  "stem": "7458.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were both members of the socialist movement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember when they used to come to visit the house, even before they married my sisters, they used to bring strange weapons that fascinated me as a child.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For instance, one of them was steel knuckles that you would put on you hand.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you were to hit somebody, you hit them with steel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Another one was springs-- heavy springs that had a ball of iron of iron at the end of it that you would swing if a fight broke out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember they used to hide them under a bed when they would come into the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And occasionally, I would sneak under and to-- to see what-- what they were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But yes, we-- things began to change drastically in the 1930s.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this brings me back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started saying that, when I was very little, my father worked in a tannery, and we lived on a little town called Wizna.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was about four years old, and that must've been in the early '30s, since I was born in '28, my father bought a tannery on the outskirts of town-- a tannery on [?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kolonyagas. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a long street of maybe two miles on the outskirts, and that played an important part in our surviving as well.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the people who sold us the tannery were Jewish people who took the money and left for Argentina.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would always discuss at home, why are we buying a tannery so that others can use the money to leave Poland?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why aren't we?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I really don't know what the answer is.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
